         <abstract id="aspace_a061bd5b9689ff9cabce3b687b93e2b0">Chiefly autographs and letters collected by Eleanor R. Belmont in connection with a copy of the Treaty of Versailles for which she wanted original signatures. There is also some personal correspondence connected with gathering the letters and a small amount of memorabilia.</abstract>
